data.title: Yogi Bear's Jellystone Park™: South Jersey, NJ
data.meta_description: Visit Jellystone Park™ South Jersey, NJ where family fun is the main attraction and memories are waiting to be made - located a short distance away from Atlantic City.
data.text:
Lucky for you, we offer some of the best camping near Atlantic City, because our Camp-Resort is located only 40 minutes away. We also offer some of the best RV camping and cabin rentals near Atlantic City, with 5+ accommodation types!

Our campground near Atlantic City is in the heart of South Jersey and has a variety of cabin & campsite options! Plus, we offer many more attractions and activities than any other campground nearby - including our beach and lake, pool, jumping pillow, sports courts, themed events, and more. These attractions, plus our friendly staff, set us apart from other South Jersey campgrounds.
